        FOTO UNIVALLE
    </div>

    <div style="width: 80%; margin: auto; align-content: center; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 50px; margin-top:50px">
        <div style=" width: 50%; height: 50%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 5px solid black; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 25px;">
